narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: I learned so much about phylogeny, the fossil record, evolutionary trends, geologic time periods, methods of organizing and interpreting molecular vs. morphological data, and everything I would want to know about vertebrates.

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: There were no weaknesses in this course. I loved it so much.

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: Yes!!! It was a little bit difficult coming into this course having never taken college-level biology, but the instructor and the TAs made it accessible for me, and I learned more than I ever thought I would. This class is absolutely fascinating, and I looked forward to every lecture and lab. Please take it.
